<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Email Sent Successfully Template." />
  <title>Email Sent Successfully</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f2f3f8;
      font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100% !important;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 570px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #edf2fb;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .divider {
      border-top: 1px solid #cecece;
      margin: 25px 0;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #1e1e2d;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .button {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5A3FC5, #402e7a);
      /* Gradient effect */
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px auto 0;
      text-align: center;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(64, 46, 122, 0.4);
      /* Soft shadow */
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Hover Effect */
    .button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6C4FD6, #5039A3);
      /* Lighter gradient */
      transform: scale(1.05);
      /* Slight scale effect */
      box-shadow: 0px 6px 14px rgba(64, 46, 122, 0.6);
    }

    /* Click Effect */
    .button:active {
      transform: scale(0.98);
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(64, 46, 122, 0.3);
    }

    /* Add subtle animated shine */
    .button::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: -100%;
      width: 300%;
      height: 300%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      transition: all 0.7s ease-in-out;
    }

    .button:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74);
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .button {
        font-size: 13px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0px 3px 8px rgba(64, 46, 122, 0.3);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div>
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="email-wrapper">
      <tr>
        <td class="header">
          <a href="https://www.inae.in/" title="logo" target="_blank">
            <img width="400" src="https://www.inae.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logon.png" alt="" />
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <div style="padding: 20px;">
            <h4 style="font-size: 18px; color: #1e1e2d; font-weight: 700;">Dear <%= salutation %> <%= userName %>,</h4>
            <div class="content">
             <p> Greetings from INAE! </p>
              <p>We are pleased to acknowledge the successful receipt of your email. Our team will be
                reviewing your message and would respond at the earliest opportunity.</p>
              <p>Should you have any additional inquiries, please do not hesitate to contact us or visit our
                  website   <a href="https://www.inae.in/contact-us/"></a> for further information.
              </p>
              <!-- <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://www.inae.in/contact-us/"></a>
              </p> -->
              <div class="divider"></div>
              <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: left;">
                With regards,<br /><br />
                Secretariat<br />
                <strong>Indian National Academy of Engineering (INAE)</strong><br />
                Ground Floor, Block-II,<br />
                Technology Bhavan,<br />
                New Mehrauli Road,<br />
                New Delhi-110 016.<br />
                Phone: 011-26582475<br />
                Website: <a href="https://www.inae.in/" style="color: #402e7a; text-decoration: none;">www.inae.in</a>
              </p>
            </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="footer">
          <p>&copy; <a href="https://www.inae.in/"
              style="color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74); text-decoration: none;"><strong>www.inae.in</strong></a></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>

</html>